Package com.erudika.para.core

Interface ParaObject

All Superinterfaces:
Linkable, Serializable, Votable
All Known Implementing Classes:
Address, App, Linker, Sysprop, Tag, Thing, Translation, User, Vote, Webhook
public interface ParaObject
extends Serializable, Linkable, Votable
The core domain interface. All Para objects implement it.
Author:
Alex Bogdanovski [alex@erudika.com]
